After a few citizens with concerning IQ have requested for a Part 2, we've done some "extensive" (not really. All you had to do is read page 2-4) research and found out that there is indeed a part 2, in a way. This is in fact a part 2 of an upload of the artist from before, but for the most part this has been a flashback to the events before Part 1 this could even be called Part 0. You can find Part 1, named Turnover, in the artist's list of uploads. 

We've already conducted a review on Part 1 some times ago, before this was upload. We recommend Part 1 as fap material to any Asuna fans. However, if you are just here for Suguha, we suggest you read it only to be filled in on the plot. Asuna is the main focus in Part 1 and Suguha does not get many pages.
